        "TileImage": "$($repository 36896e6d-cdb0-4cba-808d-74c3f564cd09).Image",
        "Description": "It seems that some people in the compound are starting to get a little paranoid about a potential assassin and have implemented a kind of &apos;buddy system&apos; - stick together, and no-one can take you out. Perhaps it&apos;s time to show them how ineffective this system is against a highly-trained ICA operative.\r\rLeave one per pair though - it&apos;ll give them something to think about.",
